Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.07,OP,,0,0,0,,在街角影照出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:23.41,OP,,0,0,0,,那寂寞的身影 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:29.00,OP,,0,0,0,,聽到 再見 這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.77,OP,,0,0,0,,完全令我無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:49.75,OP,,0,0,0,,連警報聲 也像打鼓般一下一下拷進我心裡就像引誘我流眼淚的搖籃曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,打起精神 別再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:01:01.32,OP,,0,0,0,,明天到了 一切都會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:07.00,OP,,0,0,0,,打起精神 別再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:16.27,OP,,0,0,0,,向著新吹起的風      Smile again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 再起勁點幹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼姐姐你試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典啊 祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,師傅大人別亂動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典果然好啊 真走運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那好像很有趣 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,塗鴉熊貓的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來啊 大家來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,中國三千年的詛咒畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,即將給你們看的三幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是世上最可怕最強力的詛咒畫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然後大家一定 絕對不能對別人說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,說了准沒好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,首先第一幅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一份章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好 多謝光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,來來 來來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖父 畫了這幅畫一年後就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,當時是九十二歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,第二幅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸畫了這幅畫三年後就死了當時九十八歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是客官 這只不過是開始而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你本人更可怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下一幅 下一幅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,客人看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的超大作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋老爸 把章魚燒還我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,封印…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,從畫中有什麼飛出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看你們幹的好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看你們幹的好事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,中國三千年的詛咒畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用詛咒之筆 詛咒畫軸再加上詛咒之心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在詛咒之日所畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,被詛咒了的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你們弄掉了這些畫的封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我家三代流傳的詛咒超大作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,已經被放出這世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跑出外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,OH MY GOD！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我看那簡直是中國妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是 去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 早雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,擊退妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,交給…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老爺爺也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是第三只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是第三幅超大作詛咒畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是熊貓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是抽像畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫塗鴉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣才能令他們回畫中去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,把這符貼在熊貓的額頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,飛出來的怪物就會全部回到畫上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,三隻都會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但在丑時三刻前不能令他回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物們就永遠不會回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,丑時三刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是半夜二時左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊自由了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吧 解放我的人 謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,回畫中去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 那熊貓是雌的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一看就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,難得自由了 我哭我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就今晚 就今晚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我哭我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟英俊的男朋友約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…那是我的小小夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼好像好可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且好像沒什麼危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果只是今晚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,實現夢想後 你會乖乖回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,現在老爸想的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得她好可憐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了 你的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 都是熊貓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易 好不容易夢想能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要跟這麼醜的熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒辦法啦 都沒別的熊貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,（你不覺得她好可憐嗎？）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你看那男女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,男女？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬被搶了很可恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,沒所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來 是你喜歡的章魚燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,張開口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的 好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,得寸進尺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行 我的口不能動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是氣球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個顏色好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡的顏色就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,來捉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我要捉到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,夠開心了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼只有你一個人閑著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,把符給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩了 我究竟掉在哪兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用暴力讓她回到畫上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你勸服熊貓 叫她自己回到畫上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在丑時三刻前不讓她回去的話那些怪物就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,來來 觀賞費請放入這罐中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這次是巨大熊貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,觀賞費請放這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有好厲害的演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大怪物和大魔人 還有鬼跟大僧人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,軟軟的棉花糖 真快樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能得親愛的高興 是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是個不知輕重的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,忍著點 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那只塗鴉熊貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不象話！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的 你對我的稱呼改了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去根本沒盡頭 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 你和我約定怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 說謊也是種方便 要儘早讓她對放棄回畫中去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 那人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是你 女•朋•友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 這麼粗魯又醜陋的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能是我女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候還這樣 你真這人真是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,幸運 今天竟有意外收入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再要好好努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的話是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那人不是你女朋友這事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我•好•幸•福！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好想一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還是那麼不慌不忙的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真有夠慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小靡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好辦法教你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福 幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐看到亂馬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬的話 正在後面公園做大戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我一想到這幸福時光只是剎那間的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我就很悲傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼互相喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,熊貓和人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也只是 沒結果的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只能天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 人與熊貓始終是不被承認的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我們相遇在悲傷的命運下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你能明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要我為你而為難的話是一點也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的 別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,的確比熊貓好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是意料之外的發展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是怪物的真面目嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有點 喝過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了 沒精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,同感 天道君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要洗洗溫泉爽一爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是怪物的女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 我不再理亂馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放開小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們三人已沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只有拜託亂馬加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,火中天津甘栗拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快放手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一亂馬有什麼事的話 我不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,回畫中去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,來 兩位 要回去囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次的約會 我過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又能一起坐木馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,吃棉花糖 玩氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的事 我一生也不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 能聽我的最後一次任性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,送佛送到西 只要是我能辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 吻•我•吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂吧 對方只是塗鴉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,吻別 是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 就不會有遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 難道真的要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬真害羞 那麼就由我來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,撞頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原來她希望你親額頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家來看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的超大作 給大家看看我最新大作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特別大公開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 都吃了一驚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬跟她被畫在一起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看來很幸福嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,從海岸上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,遙望得見的西瓜島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡有 九能前輩被遺忘了的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,西瓜島的交際鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:53.80,ED,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:59.14,ED,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話 這段戀情就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.65,ED,,0,0,0,,太愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:07.79,ED,,0,0,0,,不能跟你相見 但我的心情 卻追著你而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:15.64,ED,,0,0,0,,想像著你在跟什麼人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:22.75,ED,,0,0,0,,又來又往 多餘的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.41,ED,,0,0,0,,求求你 有誰能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:30.75,ED,,0,0,0,,說我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:34.43,ED,,0,0,0,,能變得幸福的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:38.68,ED,,0,0,0,,你已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.49,ED,,0,0,0,,打開未來的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:46.82,ED,,0,0,0,,只需要POSITIVE的想法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:55.84,ED,,0,0,0,,腦子是明白的 可是心卻亂了
